296
00:20:23,207 --> 00:20:25,128
There are birds and movement in the bushes.

297
00:20:25,708 --> 00:20:27,589
And as you progress, they all go silent,

298
00:20:27,749 --> 00:20:29,030
which again was all in the script.

299
00:20:29,530 --> 00:20:31,371
And then as the horrible sound,

300
00:20:31,471 --> 00:20:33,171
then the horrible sound starts coming in.

301
00:21:01,089 --> 00:21:07,675
And that loud sound you heard has a very specific purpose in this story, but I won't say what

302
00:21:07,695 --> 00:21:07,795
it is.

303
00:21:11,879 --> 00:21:16,581
So to give you a little summary with interactive narrative,

304
00:21:16,861 --> 00:21:18,921
all the different possible ways the game could sound

305
00:21:19,001 --> 00:21:20,542
is what turns it into something special.

306
00:21:21,662 --> 00:21:24,023
Just like in life, the world responds to our actions.

307
00:21:24,503 --> 00:21:25,844
It would be impossible to predict

308
00:21:25,884 --> 00:21:26,824
